features: 【Mains Extension Lead】Is your appliance power cable is too short to the socket? Our KC CABLE 2.5m extension lead will solve the short power connection problem. The 2.5m extension lead allows you to extend the socket to the area it needed to reach.

【2 Gang Extension Lead】Dual extension lead can power 2 devices. Meet daily needs, suitable for tables, floors, etc., and can also be used with extension cords of other lengths to expand the range of use.
【Double Mains Splitter】Heavy duty, 2.5M (1.5M+2X1M), H05VV-F 3*1.0MM2, 13A fused, Both side are injection molded, Tough and Fireproof, support 13A 250v, 3250W.

【Extension cords】The extension lead is perfect for using when you only have one appliance that need to power, such as monitor, laptop, printer, coffee machine and so on. ideal for using in your home, offices or even outside in your garden with waterproof box if you need the power.

【UK 3 Pin Plug Power Strip】Easy to Use, Just plug the socket in a wall outlet, long 2.5M extension lead will solve your kitchen and desktop connection problem. As the electric appliance comes almost invariably with a short cable, like as blender or flatbed scanner.
description: This heavy duty extension lead is ideal to extend the short power cable to the area you need. It can be behind your desk at the height of the table-top and extend the socket up, so you can get a bit more range out of your wired handheld tools.
